model.name: Yeast glycolysis model of Pritchard and Kell

body.pre:
From Pritchard and Kell (2002) Eur. J. Biochem. , modified from Teusink et al. (2000) Eur J Biochem 267, 5313-5329. This version uses the Vmaxes found by the best fit (R1) of Table 1 of the Pritchard and Kell paper, and simulates a decrease of external glucose concentration from 100 to 2 mM
(More model files at http://users.aber.ac.uk/lep/models.shtml)
